#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Nechronica Redux"
msgstr "Nechronica Redux"

#. ~ Description for Nechronica Redux
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"MODIFIED by YukariMindGap from Malkeus: Adds items, mutations and enemies "
"appearing in Nechronica: the Long Long Sequel."
msgstr ""
"由YukariMindGap基于Malkeus修改：添加了出现在《Nechronica: the Long Long "
"Sequel》中的物品、变异和敌人。"

#: .\nec_Armor.json
msgid "alloy trunk"
msgid_plural "alloy trunks"
msgstr[0] "合金箱"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'alloy trunk'}
#: .\nec_Armor.json
msgid ""
"A metal trunk. Not to mention storage, because it is sturdy it becomes a "
"shield substitute. You can use it as a weapon that swings around by taking "
"advantage of its weight."
msgstr "一个金属箱。除了储物功能外，因其坚固耐用，还可作为盾牌的替代品。利用其重量，你可以把它当作挥舞的武器。"

#: .\nec_Armor.json
msgid "coffin backpack"
msgid_plural "coffin backpacks"
msgstr[0] "棺材背包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'coffin backpack'}
#: .\nec_Armor.json
msgid ""
"A coffin with a long chain connected to it. Unwieldy to wear, but offers a "
"huge space for your items. It also doubles as a shield on your back."
msgstr "一口连接着长链的棺材。穿戴起来笨重不便，但能为你的物品提供巨大的存储空间。同时，它还能充当背部的盾牌。"

#: .\nec_Armor.json
msgid "ribbon"
msgid_plural "ribbons"
msgstr[0] "缎带"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ribbon', 'str_pl': 'ribbons'}
#: .\nec_Armor.json
msgid ""
"A small cute cloth ribbon. There is no defensive power, but may heal you in "
"this ruined world."
msgstr "一条小巧可爱的布质缎带。它没有防御能力，但在这个破败的世界里，或许能治愈你。"

#: .\nec_Armor.json
msgid "companion teddy bear"
msgid_plural "companion teddy bears"
msgstr[0] "伙伴泰迪熊"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'companion teddy bear'}
#: .\nec_Armor.json
msgid ""
"A cute stuffed toy attached to your body. Offers no support other than "
"morale."
msgstr "一个附着在你身上的可爱填充玩具。除了提升士气外，不提供任何实际支持。"

#: .\nec_Armor.json
msgid "gothic lolita dress"
msgid_plural "gothic lolita dresss"
msgstr[0] "哥特洛丽塔连衣裙"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gothic lolita dress'}
#: .\nec_Armor.json
msgid ""
"An impractically lacy dress from the Gothic Lolita subculture. Despite all "
"the laces, it is surprisingly easy to move in."
msgstr "一件来自哥特洛丽塔亚文化、装饰繁复不实用的蕾丝连衣裙。尽管满是蕾丝，但活动起来却出奇地方便。"

#: .\nec_Armor.json
msgid "gothic lolita headdress"
msgid_plural "gothic lolita headdresss"
msgstr[0] "哥特洛丽塔头饰"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gothic lolita headdress'}
#: .\nec_Armor.json
msgid ""
"A lacy headdress meant to be worn with the dress. It attracts attention."
msgstr "一顶蕾丝头饰，旨在与连衣裙搭配穿戴。它能吸引注意力。"

#: .\nec_Armor.json
msgid "survivor gothic lolita dress"
msgid_plural "survivor gothic lolita dresss"
msgstr[0] "幸存者哥特洛丽塔连衣裙"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor gothic lolita dress'}
#: .\nec_Armor.json
msgid ""
"A gothic lolita dress made practical with kevlar and pockets. The skirt "
"allows a medium-sized firearm to be holstered. It is a bit stuffy in the "
"chest area, hoever."
msgstr "一件用凯夫拉材料和口袋改造得实用的哥特洛丽塔连衣裙。裙摆允许插放一把中型枪械。不过，胸部区域有点闷热。"

#: .\nec_Armor.json
msgid "pannier"
msgid_plural "panniers"
msgstr[0] "裙撑"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pannier'}
#: .\nec_Armor.json
msgid ""
"An underskirt meant to be worn under a dress. It keeps the skirt puffy by "
"way of wires."
msgstr "一件设计穿在连衣裙下面的衬裙。它通过金属丝保持裙摆蓬松。"

#: .\nec_bionics.json
msgid "Remote Attack"
msgid_plural "Remote Attacks"
msgstr[0] "远程攻击"

#: .\nec_bionics.json
msgid "Dummy item.  If you see this, then something went wrong."
msgstr "虚拟物品。如果你看到这个，说明出了点问题。"

#: .\nec_bionics.json
msgctxt "gun_type_type"
msgid "rifle"
msgstr "步枪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Remote Attack'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Remote Attack CBM'}
#: .\nec_bionics.json
msgid ""
"Your arms and legs come off and attack the opponent. Since they return "
"automatically after the attack, you do not have to worry about removing it."
msgstr "你的手臂和腿会脱离身体攻击对手。由于攻击后会自动返回，你不必担心需要手动移除它们。"

#: .\nec_bionics.json
msgid "Remote Attack CBM"
msgid_plural "Remote Attack CBMs"
msgstr[0] "远程攻击 CBM"

#: .\nec_bionics.json
msgid "Pile bunker"
msgid_plural "Pile bunkers"
msgstr[0] "桩击器"

#: .\nec_bionics.json
msgctxt "gun_type_type"
msgid "shotgun"
msgstr "霰弹枪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Pile bunker'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Pile bunker CBM'}
#: .\nec_bionics.json
msgid ""
"The metallic stake stored in the forearm shoots with high vibration and "
"super high speed. Although you need to approach to close range, that power "
"is guaranteed. Of course, it also consumes electricity."
msgstr "储存在前臂的金属桩会以高频振动和超高速射出。虽然你需要接近到近距离，但其威力有保证。当然，它也会消耗电力。"

#: .\nec_bionics.json
msgid "Pile bunker CBM"
msgid_plural "Pile bunker CBMs"
msgstr[0] "桩击器 CBM"

#: .\nec_bionics.json
msgid "Drill"
msgid_plural "Drills"
msgstr[0] "钻头"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Drill'}
#: .\nec_bionics.json
msgid ""
"This transforms your wrist in to a drill head. You will be able to make a "
"hole in everything."
msgstr "这会将你的手腕变形为钻头。你将能在任何东西上钻孔。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Drill'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Drill CBM'}
#: .\nec_bionics.json
msgid ""
"Embed the deformation mechanism from the wrist to the drill head. It "
"consumes electric power and starts high-speed rotation. You can excavate "
"both the ground and zombies."
msgstr "将变形机制从手腕嵌入到钻头。它消耗电力并开始高速旋转。你既可以挖掘地面，也能对付僵尸。"

#: .\nec_bionics.json
msgid "Drill CBM"
msgid_plural "Drill CBMs"
msgstr[0] "钻头 CBM"

#: .\nec_bionics.json
msgid "Lightsaber"
msgid_plural "Lightsabers"
msgstr[0] "光剑"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Lightsaber'}
#: .\nec_bionics.json
msgid "This is a lightsaber. KWISHUUUU KWISHUUUU."
msgstr "这是一把光剑。咻咻咻咻咻咻。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Lightsaber'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Lightsaber CBM'}
#: .\nec_bionics.json
msgid ""
"Embed the mechanism that generates the light blade in the arm. It becomes a "
"powerful weapon by starting as necessary."
msgstr "将生成光刃的机制嵌入手臂。在需要时启动，它将成为强大的武器。"

#: .\nec_bionics.json
msgid "Lightsaber CBM"
msgid_plural "Lightsaber CBMs"
msgstr[0] "光剑 CBM"

#: .\nec_book.json
msgid "PE105 \"Necromantic\": Observation"
msgid_plural "PE105 \"Necromantic\": Observation"
msgstr[0] "PE105 \"死灵术\"：观察记录"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'PE105 "Necromantic": Observation', 'str_pl':
#. 'PE105 "Necromantic": Observation'}
#: .\nec_book.json
msgid ""
"This sheets of paper dated 10 days before all this started-describes a "
"complex chemical formula and a diagram to embed something like slime mold in"
" humans..."
msgstr "这些纸张的日期标注在这场灾难开始的十天前——上面描述了一种复杂的化学公式和一张示意图，关于如何将类似黏菌的东西植入人体……"

#: .\nec_dreams.json
msgid ""
"In your dream, your body got cut, but you didn't consider it a problem."
msgstr "在梦中，你的身体被切割，但你并未将其视为问题。"

#: .\nec_dreams.json
msgid "You had a dream where something was wriggling inside your body."
msgstr "你做了一个梦，梦中有东西在你体内蠕动。"

#: .\nec_dreams.json
msgid "In your dream, you were reconnecting your dismembered arms."
msgstr "在梦中，你正在重新连接自己被肢解的手臂。"

#: .\nec_dreams.json
msgid ""
"A big hole opened in your face as you looked in the mirror ... .... Ah, it "
"was just a dream."
msgstr "当你照镜子时，脸上裂开了一个大洞……啊，原来只是个梦。"

#: .\nec_dreams.json
msgid ""
"You had such a strange and crisp dream, that you were embracing your own "
"head."
msgstr "你做了一个如此怪异而清晰的梦，梦见自己正拥抱着自己的头颅。"

#: .\nec_dreams.json
msgid ""
"You had a terrifying dream where someone was doing a transplant on something"
" not human."
msgstr "你做了一个可怕的梦，梦中有人正在对非人之物进行移植手术。"

#: .\nec_dreams.json
msgid ""
"In your dream, you were spoken to by an unknown person who is right next to "
"you. When you turn you notice their head is connected to your body."
msgstr "在梦中，一个紧挨着你的陌生人向你说话。当你转身时，你发现他们的头颅连接在你的身体上。"

#: .\nec_dreams.json
msgid ""
"I woke up from a dream where I was packing my own torn-out intenstines back "
"into my body. Maybe I should stop packing weird things into myself."
msgstr "我从一个梦中醒来，梦里我正在将自己被扯出的肠子塞回体内。也许我该停止往自己身体里塞奇怪的东西了。"

#: .\nec_gun.json
msgid "quad double-barrel pipe shotgun"
msgid_plural "quad double-barrel pipe shotguns"
msgstr[0] "四联双管管道霰弹枪"

#: .\nec_gun.json
msgid ""
"A home-made shotgun made from four double-barrel shotguns joined together. "
"It has eight times the power of a pipe shotgun. Legend says that the first "
"person to craft this was inspired by a certain movie about the undead."
msgstr "一把由四把双管霰弹枪组合而成的自制霰弹枪。其威力是普通管道霰弹枪的八倍。传说中，第一个制作出这把枪的人，灵感来源于某部关于不死生物的电影。"

#: .\nec_gun.json
msgid "single"
msgstr "单发"

#: .\nec_gun.json
msgid "double"
msgstr "双发"

#: .\nec_gun.json
msgid "auto"
msgstr "自动"

#: .\nec_martial_arts_manuals.json
msgid "Kung Fu for Dummies"
msgid_plural "Kung Fu for Dummiess"
msgstr[0] "功夫入门指南"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Kung Fu for Dummies'}
#: .\nec_martial_arts_manuals.json
msgid "A complete guide to Kung Fu."
msgstr "一本完整的功夫指南。"

#: .\nec_martialarts.json
msgid "Kung Fu"
msgstr "功夫"

#. ~ Description for martial art '{'str': 'Kung Fu'}'
#: .\nec_martialarts.json
msgid ""
"Kung Fu is a kind of martial art, but it is also means - Skill achieved "
"through hard work - in traditional Chinese. It is characterized by hard "
"striking and flexible body handling, it is good at knocking your opponent "
"off their feet."
msgstr "功夫是一种武术，但在传统中文里，它也意味着——通过艰苦努力获得的技能。其特点是刚猛的打击和灵活的身体操控，擅长将对手击倒在地。"

#. ~ Initiate message for martial art '{'str': 'Kung Fu'}'
#: .\nec_martialarts.json
msgid "You stand and become vigilant against attacks *"
msgstr "你站定身形，警惕攻击*"

#. ~ Initiate message for martial art '{'str': 'Kung Fu'}'
#: .\nec_martialarts.json
#, c-format
msgid "%s stands tell ande become vigilant"
msgstr "%s 站定身形，变得警惕"

#: .\nec_martialarts.json
msgid "Kung fu breath"
msgstr "功夫吐纳"

#. ~ Description of buff 'Kung fu breath' for martial art '{'str': 'Kung Fu'}'
#: .\nec_martialarts.json
msgid ""
"You can always keep calm by a unique breathing method. Bonus for avoidance "
"and blow"
msgstr "通过独特的呼吸法，你总能保持冷静。提升闪避与打击能力。"

#: .\nec_martialarts.json
msgid "Kung fu move"
msgstr "功夫步法"

#. ~ Description of buff 'Kung fu move' for martial art '{'str': 'Kung Fu'}'
#: .\nec_martialarts.json
msgid ""
"Using footwork you can always turn to attack and avoid. Bonus to hit and "
"avoid"
msgstr "运用步法，你总能转身攻击与闪避。提升命中与闪避能力。"

#: .\nec_martialarts.json
msgid "Kung fu dodge"
msgstr "功夫闪避"

#. ~ Description of buff 'Kung fu dodge' for martial art '{'str': 'Kung Fu'}'
#: .\nec_martialarts.json
msgid ""
"The moment of avoiding the attack is not necessarily a chance. Always hear "
"the gap of counterattack. Bonus for avoidance and blow. Duplicate possible"
msgstr "闪避攻击的瞬间未必是机会。总能听到反击的间隙。提升闪避与打击能力。可叠加。"

#: .\nec_martialarts.json
msgid "Niten Ichi-Ryu"
msgstr "二天一流"

#: .\nec_martialarts.json
msgid "Krav Maga"
msgstr "以色列格斗术"

#: .\nec_martialarts.json
msgid "Fencing"
msgstr "击剑术"

#: .\nec_martialarts.json
msgid "Medieval Swordsmanship"
msgstr "中世纪剑术"

#: .\nec_martialarts.json
msgid "Ninjutsu"
msgstr "忍术"

#: .\nec_monsters.json
msgid "zombie queen"
msgid_plural "zombie queens"
msgstr[0] "僵尸女王"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'zombie queen'}
#: .\nec_monsters.json
msgid ""
"It looks like a beautiful girl, but is actually the queen of the undead who "
"leads countless undead."
msgstr "她看起来像一位美丽的少女，实则是统领无数不死生物的亡灵女王。"

#: .\nec_monsters.json
msgid "little zombie queen"
msgid_plural "little zombie queens"
msgstr[0] "小僵尸女王"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'little zombie queen'}
#: .\nec_monsters.json
msgid "It looks like a beautiful girl, but is really...?"
msgstr "她看起来像一位美丽的少女，但真的是……？"

#: .\nec_monsters.json
msgid "banshee"
msgid_plural "banshees"
msgstr[0] "报丧女妖"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'banshee'}
#: .\nec_monsters.json
msgid ""
"Originally it looked like a girl, but now her ego collapsed she's gone mad."
msgstr "原本她看起来像个女孩，但如今自我崩溃，已然疯狂。"

#: .\nec_monsters.json
msgid "nemesis"
msgid_plural "nemesiss"
msgstr[0] "复仇女神"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nemesis'}
#: .\nec_monsters.json
msgid ""
"Has the appearance of a girl, but it is swinging a knife with obvious "
"superhuman speed and strength. There is no doubt that it is reinforced with "
"blaspheming techniques."
msgstr "外表看似少女，却以明显超人的速度与力量挥舞着刀刃。毫无疑问，它经过了亵渎技术的强化。"

#: .\nec_monsters.json
msgid "valkyrie"
msgid_plural "valkyries"
msgstr[0] "女武神"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'valkyrie'}
#: .\nec_monsters.json
msgid ""
"It was mostly horrible machine remodeling that kept the prototype of the "
"human body intact. It has no legs and is floating with something like a "
"floater."
msgstr "这主要是可怕的机械改造，但保留了人体原型的基本形态。它没有双腿，依靠类似浮游装置的东西悬浮移动。"

#: .\nec_monsters.json
msgid "chimera"
msgid_plural "chimeras"
msgstr[0] "奇美拉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'chimera'}
#: .\nec_monsters.json
msgid ""
"It looks like a human being, but the limbs are cut, and instead there is a "
"monster with things like hooks attached. Seems to have high regenerative "
"power, but as there is no eyes it has no vision"
msgstr "它看起来像人类，但四肢被切除，取而代之的是附着钩状物的怪物。似乎拥有高再生能力，但由于没有眼睛，它不具备视觉。"

#: .\nec_mutagen.json
msgid "necromantic serum"
msgid_plural "necromantic serums"
msgstr[0] "死灵血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'necromantic serum'}
#: .\nec_mutagen.json
msgid ""
"A super-concentrated mutagen that resembles a liquified corpse. You need a "
"syringe to inject it...  if you really want to?"
msgstr "一种超浓缩的诱变剂，看起来像液化尸体。你需要注射器来注入它……如果你真的想这么做？"

#: .\nec_mutagen.json
msgid "necromantic mutagen"
msgid_plural "necromantic mutagens"
msgstr[0] "死灵诱变剂"

#. ~ Mutation class name
#: .\nec_mutation_category.json .\nec_mutations.json
msgid "Undead"
msgstr "不死生物"

#. ~ Mutation class: Undead mutagen_message
#: .\nec_mutation_category.json
msgid "Your heart slows down for a beat."
msgstr "你的心跳漏了一拍。"

#. ~ Mutation class: Undead iv_message
#: .\nec_mutation_category.json
msgid "Your feel that all your pain is gone for a moment."
msgstr "你感觉所有的疼痛瞬间消失了。"

#. ~ Mutation class: Undead Male memorial messsage
#: .\nec_mutation_category.json
msgctxt "memorial_male"
msgid "Couldn't pull themselves together."
msgstr "无法振作起来。"

#. ~ Mutation class: Undead Female memorial messsage
#: .\nec_mutation_category.json
msgctxt "memorial_female"
msgid "Couldn't pull themselves together."
msgstr "无法振作起来。"

#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid "Trap"
msgstr "陷阱"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Trap'}
#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your body is a young girl, but you also have male features. Although it is "
"rare, it will not be useful any longer."
msgstr "你的身体是少女，但也具有男性特征。虽然罕见，但这不再有任何用处。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Undead'}
#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid ""
"The collapsed body is broken and patchy. Even if it breaks, you can simply "
"reattach the parts."
msgstr "坍塌的身体破碎且斑驳。即使断裂，你也可以简单地重新接合部件。"

#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid "Extra Eyes"
msgstr "额外眼睛"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Extra Eyes'}
#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid ""
"A new eye came out of your body. The field of view broadens, but the "
"appearance is disgusting. +2 Perception"
msgstr "你的身体长出了一只新眼睛。视野扩大了，但外观令人作呕。+2 感知"

#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid "Extra Arms"
msgstr "额外手臂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Extra Arms'}
#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid ""
"You no longer have just two arms. There are additional arms on your "
"shoulder. It is hard to master, but you may expand your range of tactics. "
"Dex + 2"
msgstr "你不再只有两只手臂。肩膀上长出了额外的手臂。难以掌握，但你可能扩展战术范围。敏捷 + 2"

#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid "Extra legs"
msgstr "额外腿部"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Extra legs'}
#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid ""
"You now have more than two legs. Another pair of legs are growing from your "
"waist. You will not be able to equip usual leg protection, but you can move "
"fast."
msgstr "你现在不止两条腿。腰部又长出了一对腿。你将无法装备通常的腿部防护，但可以快速移动。"

#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid "Large Hole"
msgstr "巨大空洞"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Large Hole'}
#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid ""
"There is a big hole in your body. However, there is no hindrance to battle, "
"and the person who saw it is a little surprised."
msgstr "你的身体上有一个大洞。然而，这对战斗没有妨碍，看到它的人会有点惊讶。"

#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid "Horns"
msgstr "犄角"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Horns'}
#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid ""
"Large protuberances are growing from your body. It will be enough to pierce "
"and hook at close range."
msgstr "巨大的突起物正从你的身体长出。足以在近距离穿刺和钩挂。"

#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid "You stab %s with your horns."
msgstr "你用犄角刺穿了 %s。"

#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid "%1$s stabs %2$s with their horns."
msgstr "%1$s 用他们的犄角刺穿了 %2$s。"

#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid "Elongated Tongue"
msgstr "长舌"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Elongated Tongue'}
#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid "Your tongue has become long and tubular. Not particularly effective."
msgstr "你的舌头变得又长又管状。效果并不特别显著。"

#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid "Prehensile Tongue"
msgstr "灵巧之舌"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Prehensile Tongue'}
#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your tongue is dripping with drool. You can not equip anything on your "
"mouth, but they will be surprised when you attack them with your tongue."
msgstr "你的舌头滴着口水。你无法在嘴上装备任何物品，但当你用舌头攻击时，它们会大吃一惊。"

#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid "You attack %s with your tongue."
msgstr "你用舌头攻击了%s。"

#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid "%1$s attacks %2$s with their tongue."
msgstr "%1$s用舌头攻击了%2$s。"

#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid "Failing"
msgstr "崩坏中"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Failing'}
#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid "Your body starts breaking apart. You become more encumbered and frail."
msgstr "你的身体开始分崩离析。你变得更加笨重和脆弱。"

#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid "Torn Membrane"
msgstr "撕裂之膜"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Torn Membrane'}
#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid ""
"A membrane of deadly flesh, the wing of the fallen angel. Although you can "
"not fly, a wing protects your body from attacks."
msgstr "一片致命的血肉之膜，堕落天使的翅膀。虽然你无法飞翔，但这只翅膀能保护你的身体免受攻击。"

#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid "Extra Head"
msgstr "额外头颅"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Extra Head'}
#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid ""
"There is another head on your shoulders. And here you thought you were doing"
" well with just one. You can not see the other side of the face directly, "
"but you can understand what you see over there. +5 Intelligence, +3 "
"Perception"
msgstr "你的肩膀上多了一个头。你还以为只有一个头就够用了呢。你无法直接看到另一侧的脸，但你能理解那边看到的东西。+5智力，+3感知"

#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid "Crumbling"
msgstr "瓦解"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Crumbling'}
#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your body is coming apart at its seams. You become even more encumbered and "
"frail."
msgstr "你的身体正在接缝处裂开。你变得更加笨重和脆弱。"

#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid "Patchwork"
msgstr "拼凑之躯"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Patchwork'}
#: .\nec_mutations.json
msgid ""
"You can conveniently change your body. Although it will be slightly weaker "
"against attacks, the overall encumbrance is relaxed considerably."
msgstr "你可以方便地更换身体。虽然对攻击的抵抗力会稍弱一些，但整体负重显著减轻。"

#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Stacy Doll"
msgstr "斯泰西人偶"

#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Stacy Doll"
msgstr "斯泰西人偶"

#. ~ Profession (male Stacy Doll) description
#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You are a doll, a result of occult reanimation on human corpses. You are the"
" most basic of the dolls, but comes equipped with useful skills and "
"utilities."
msgstr "你是一个人偶，是人体尸体经过神秘复活术的产物。你是最基础的人偶，但配备了有用的技能和工具。"

#. ~ Profession (female Stacy Doll) description
#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"You are a doll, a result of occult reanimation on human corpses. You are the"
" most basic of the dolls, but comes equipped with useful skills and "
"utilities."
msgstr "你是一个人偶，是人体尸体经过神秘复活术的产物。你是最基础的人偶，但配备了有用的技能和工具。"

