msgstr "安魂人偶"

#. ~ Profession (male Requiem Doll) description
#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You are a doll, a result of occult reanimation on human corpses. Your "
"previous experience with firearms came handy in your now-undeath."
msgstr "你是一个人偶，是人体尸体经过神秘复活术的产物。你生前使用火器的经验在如今的不死之身中派上了用场。"

#. ~ Profession (female Requiem Doll) description
#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"You are a doll, a result of occult reanimation on human corpses. Your "
