msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Thanatos Doll"
msgstr "塔纳托斯人偶"

#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Thanatos Doll"
msgstr "塔纳托斯人偶"

#. ~ Profession (male Thanatos Doll) description
#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You are a doll, a result of occult reanimation on human corpses. A tough "
"combatant able to take on the biggest of threats in close combat."
msgstr "你是一个人偶，是人体尸体经过神秘复活术的产物。你是一名坚韧的战士，能够近身对抗最强大的威胁。"

