#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Gothic Doll"
msgstr "哥特人偶"

#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Gothic Doll"
msgstr "哥特人偶"

#. ~ Profession (male Gothic Doll) description
#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You are a doll, a result of occult reanimation on human corpses. You were "
"designed to hunt down the other undead and devour them."
msgstr "你是一个人偶，是人体尸体经过神秘复活术的产物。你被设计用来猎杀其他不死生物并吞噬它们。"

#. ~ Profession (female Gothic Doll) description
#: .\nec_professions.json
