msgstr "你是一个人偶，是人体尸体经过神秘复活术的产物。你被设计用来猎杀其他不死生物并吞噬它们。"

#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Erudite Doll"
msgstr "博学人偶"

#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Erudite Doll"
msgstr "博学人偶"

#. ~ Profession (male Erudite Doll) description
#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You are a doll, a result of occult reanimation on human corpses. You have "
"the skills to utilize explosives and a proper discipline on its usage."
msgstr "你是一个人偶，是人体尸体经过神秘复活术的产物。你拥有使用爆炸物的技能，并对其使用有严格的纪律。"

#. ~ Profession (female Erudite Doll) description
#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"You are a doll, a result of occult reanimation on human corpses. You have "
"the skills to utilize explosives and a proper discipline on its usage."
msgstr "你是一个人偶，是人体尸体经过神秘复活术的产物。你拥有使用爆炸物的技能，并对其使用有严格的纪律。"

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"Let's have a long talk.\""
msgstr "\"让我们好好谈谈。\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"Welcome to the story of the miniature garden.\""
msgstr "\"欢迎来到微型花园的故事。\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"Let's enjoy the dance of distortion.\""
msgstr "\"让我们享受扭曲之舞吧。\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"Did you listen to the play?\""
msgstr "\"你听了那场戏吗？\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"Let's have another tea party.\""
msgstr "\"让我们再开一次茶会吧。\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"What is that ringing bell? I wish it would stop.\""
msgstr "\"那是什么铃声？真希望它能停下。\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"Let's make your doll.\""
msgstr "\"让我们来制作你的人偶吧。\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"I do not mind failure. You ARE dead after all.\""
msgstr "\"我不介意失败。毕竟你已经死了。\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"Dolls are lovely things.\""
msgstr "\"人偶是可爱的东西。\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"Let the curtain rise and the dead dance.\""
msgstr "\"让帷幕升起，让死者起舞。\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"... A tin of chicken dumplings? ...\""
msgstr "\"……一罐鸡肉饺子？……\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"Welcome to the beautiful nightmare.\""
msgstr "\"欢迎来到这美丽的噩梦。\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"Please humiliate and destroy it.\""
msgstr "\"请羞辱并摧毁它。\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"Get the ten sided dice.\""
msgstr "\"拿十面骰来。\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"Now it is time to show you how it is done.\""
msgstr "\"现在是时候向你展示如何做到了。\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"I am completely beautiful!\""
msgstr "\"我真是美极了！\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"Oh, those of girls are disgusting people!\""
msgstr "\"哦，那些女孩真是令人作呕！\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"I'm not supposed to be complete, just elegant.\""
msgstr "\"我不需要完美，只需优雅。\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"I am the supreme and solitary necromancer!\""
msgstr "\"我是至高无上且孤独的死灵法师！\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"That is such a crock of...\""
msgstr "\"那真是胡扯……\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"I am the last necromancer you will ever see.\""
msgstr "\"我是你将会见到的最后一位死灵法师。\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"OooooOooooOooo...\""
msgstr "\"呜哦哦哦哦哦哦……\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"You think you are lucky?\""
msgstr "\"你以为自己很幸运吗？\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"Muha... Muhahaha.... MUHAHAHAHAHAHA!\""
msgstr "\"唔哈……唔哈哈哈……唔哈哈哈哈哈哈！\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"(Sings a song)\""
msgstr "\"（唱起歌来）\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"Haha, a hundred sided dice.\""
msgstr "\"哈哈，一百面骰。\""

#: .\nec_techniques.json
