#: .\nec_tool.json
msgid "great knife"
msgid_plural "great knifes"
msgstr[0] "巨型刀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'great knife'}
#: .\nec_tool.json
msgid ""
"A massively oversized knife. It is not very good at delicate works, but its "
"primary function is second to none."
msgstr "一把尺寸过大的刀。它不擅长精细工作，但其主要功能无与伦比。"

#: .\nec_tool.json
msgid "monomolecular fiber"
msgid_plural "monomolecular fibers"
msgstr[0] "单分子纤维"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'monomolecular fiber'}
#: .\nec_tool.json
msgid ""
"A thin, surprisingly sharp wire. It is used as a very sharp garrote capable "
"of dismembering enemies precisely."
msgstr "一根纤细却异常锋利的金属丝。它被用作极其锋利的绞索，能够精准地肢解敌人。"

#: .\nec_tool.json
msgid "giant scissors"
msgid_plural "giant scissorss"
msgstr[0] "巨型剪刀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'giant scissors'}
#: .\nec_tool.json
msgid ""
"A huge pair of scissors for battle. It is difficult to walk around with, but"
" its ruggedness and overwhelming cutting force are attractive."
msgstr "用于战斗的巨大剪刀。携带行走不便，但其坚固性和压倒性的剪切力颇具吸引力。"

#: .\nec_tool.json
msgid "superior katana"
msgid_plural "superior katanas"
msgstr[0] "精良武士刀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'superior katana'}
#: .\nec_tool.json
msgid ""
"An improved version of the katana. Inscription is carved with a sword that "
"was forged by high technology."
msgstr "武士刀的改良版本。刀身上刻有铭文，由高科技锻造而成。"

#: .\nec_tool.json
msgid "iron ball and chain"
msgid_plural "iron ball and chains"
msgstr[0] "铁球链枷"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'iron ball and chain'}
#: .\nec_tool.json
msgid ""
"A brutal weapon that is basically a metal ball attached to a chain. Not only"
" it is capable of dealing crushing blows, it can be used to entangle "
"enemies."
msgstr "一种残忍的武器，本质上是一个连接在链条上的金属球。不仅能造成粉碎性打击，还可用于缠绕敌人。"

#: .\nec_tool.json
msgid "flying guillotine"
msgid_plural "flying guillotines"
msgstr[0] "飞铡"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'flying guillotine'}
#: .\nec_tool.json
msgid ""
"A brutal weapon that is basically a saw-blade attached to a chain. Its "
"sharpness and long length allows swift decapitation."
msgstr "一种残忍的武器，本质上是一个连接在链条上的锯刃。其锋利度和长距离允许快速斩首。"

#: .\nec_tool.json
msgid "combat lawnmower (off)"
msgid_plural "combat lawnmowers (off)"
msgstr[0] "战斗割草机（关闭）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'combat lawnmower (off)', 'str_pl': 'combat
#. lawnmowers (off)'}.
#: .\nec_tool.json
msgid "The screw starts its terrifying rotation with a loud sound!"
msgstr "螺丝伴随着巨响开始恐怖的旋转！"

#. ~ Use action need_charges_msg for {'str': 'combat lawnmower (off)',
#. 'str_pl': 'combat lawnmowers (off)'}.
#: .\nec_tool.json
msgid "You pull on the cord for a while... but nothing happens."
msgstr "你拉了一会儿启动绳……但什么都没发生。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'combat lawnmower (off)', 'str_pl': 'combat
#. lawnmowers (off)'}
#: .\nec_tool.json
msgid ""
"A modified lawn mower used to mow down zombies. When turning on the switch, "
"its blades start spinning waiting for their victims."
msgstr "一台改装过的割草机，用于收割僵尸。打开开关时，其刀片开始旋转，等待受害者。"

#: .\nec_tool.json
msgid "combat lawnmower (on)"
msgid_plural "combat lawnmowers (on)"
msgstr[0] "战斗割草机（开启）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'combat lawnmower (on)', 'str_pl': 'combat
#. lawnmowers (on)'}.
#: .\nec_tool.json
msgid "The screw slowly stops rotating."
msgstr "螺丝慢慢停止了旋转。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'combat lawnmower (on)', 'str_pl': 'combat
#. lawnmowers (on)'}
#: .\nec_tool.json
msgid ""
"A combat lawnmower that has been activated. Its spinning blades will slice "
"through anything in its way."
msgstr "一台已激活的战斗割草机。其旋转的刀片将切碎路径上的一切。"

#: .\nec_tool.json
msgid "wrist-mounted hidden blade"
msgid_plural "wrist-mounted hidden blades"
msgstr[0] "腕部隐藏刀刃"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'wrist-mounted hidden blade'}
#: .\nec_tool.json
msgid ""
"A small sword with a popping mechanism stored inside the glove. It was able "
"to store and deploy instantaneously, and it was heavily used to assassinate "
"key people."
msgstr "一把带有弹出机制的小型剑，储存在手套内。它能瞬间收纳和部署，曾被广泛用于刺杀关键人物。"
